Template B√°sico para tu T&C:
markdown# Terms of Service - YageCoin

## 1. Service Description
YageCoin is a cryptocurrency aggregator platform. We DO NOT:
- Hold or custody user funds
- Execute transactions directly
- Provide financial advice
